### 8.6 List configs by station
GET {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/device-connections?stationId=STATION_001

### 8.7 Get config by id
GET {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/device-connections/{{createDeviceConnection.response.body.data.id}}
